<font color="#FF0000">ARE THERE ANY REAL MEN LEFT?</font><br>
<tt>Thu Dec 18 23:05:20 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Paul, if your friends will let you talk, you perhaps, are my last resource. I want to know about vets, not about hate filled whatever's who seem to control this site. You seem to be on the edge of their grip.<br><br>
Are you?<br><br>
I want to learn about what the real war in Viet Nam was like, and how and why my brother died in a friendly fire air strike. But I want to know why he thought he had to be there, my parents can't tell me, I hoped someone here could. <br>
But so far, I have been insulted, called spatz, called this and that, and not given the time of day or the right answer. What is with your friends?<br><br>
Talk to me via e mail if you don't want them to turn on you, which seems to be the model here.  This place is like a spider trap, you hit one tripwire and the whole place comes down on you. Real brave men.  God, I knew the war made for some head cases, but I never experienced what I have in the last 3 days since I found this place.  Are you part of it?<br>
We will see.  I hope the rest of you find the peace you never have found yet, at least at your own expense, and for the one who returned my questions into a vile and disgusting e mail, thinking I was spatz, I only pity you, and god forbid, your children.  I hope you are not married or have any, but your type usually has large families. A unfortunate fact Darwin forgot to factor in.
